<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Subscription Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #f48c42;
            text-weight: bold;
        }
        .content {
            text-align: center;
        }
        .content h2 {
            color: #f48c42;
        }
        .content p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 20px;
        }
        .footer p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #888;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Event Sphere</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Welcome Aboard!</h2>
            <p>Hey {{ firstName }},</p>
            <p>We're thrilled to have you join our event <strong>{{ eventTitle }}</strong>! Get ready for an amazing time.</p>
            <p>Here's what you need to know:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Event:</strong> {{ eventTitle }}</li>
                <li><strong>Date & Time:</strong> {{ eventDateTime|date('M d, Y H:i') }}</li>
                <li><strong>Max Participants:</strong> {{ maxParticipants }}</li>
            </ul>
            <p>We can't wait to see you there!</p>
            <p><em>P.S. Don't forget to bring your smile :)</em></p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 EventSphere. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
